nn#The Beach Boys version|Barbara Ann]]\" by [[The Beach Boys]], \"[[As Tears Go By (song)|As Tears Go By]]\" / \"[[19th Nervous Breakdown]]\" by [[The Rolling Stones]], \"[[Michelle (song)#Cover versions|Michelle]]\" by [[The Overlanders (band)|The Overlanders]], \"[[Elusive Butterfly]]\" by [[Bob Lind]], \"[[You Don't Have to Say You Love Me]]\" by [[Dusty Springfield]], \"[[Il ragazzo della via Gluck#International covers|Tar and Cement]]\" by [[Verdelle Smith (singer)|Verdelle Smith]],  \"[[Bus Stop (song)|Bus Stop]]\" by [[The Hollies]], \"[[Lara's Theme|Somewhere, My Love]]\" (Theme from [[Doctor Zhivago (film)|Doctor Zhivago]]) by [[Ray Coniff#The Ray Coniff Signers|The Ray Coniff Signers]], \"Step Back\" / \"Cara-Lyn\" by [[Johnny Young]] and Kompany, and \"Needle in a Haystack\" / \"I Won't Be the Same Without Her\" by [[The Twilights]].\n\nOther hits (with their peak positions noted) were \"Love Letter\" / \"\n[[Dancing in the Street]]\" by [[Billy Thorpe and the Aztecs]] (3), \"[[The Sound of Silence]]\" by [[Simon & Garfunkel]] (3), \"[[Listen People]]\" by [[Herman's Hermits]] (3), \"Come and See Her\" / \"I Can See\" by [[The Easybeats]] (3), \"[[Pretty Flamingo]]\" by [[Manfred Mann]] (3), \"Born a Woman\" by [[Judy Stone]] (3), \"[[Black Is Black]]\" by [[Los Bravos]] (3), \"Women (Make You Feel Alright)\" / \"In My Book\" by [[The Easybeats]] (4), \"[[A Must to Avoid]]\" by [[Herman's Hermits]] (4), \"Tennessee Waltz Song\" / \"I Am What I Am\" by [[Ray Brown and The Whispers]] (4), \"Someday, One Day\" by [[The Seekers]] (4), \"[[Monday, Monday]]\" by [[The Mamas and the Papas|The Mamas & The Papas]] (4), \"[[Sunshine Superman]]\" by [[Donovan]] (4), \"[[They're Coming to Take Me Away, Ha-Haaa!]]\" by [[Napoleon XIV]] (4), \"I'm a Man\" by [[The Yardbirds]] (5), \"[[The Pied Piper]]\" by [[Crispian St. Peters]] (5), \"[[Second Hand Rose (song)|Second Hand Rose]]\" by [[Barbra Streisand]] (6), \"[[Li'l Red Riding Hood]]\" by [[Sam the Sham]] and The 