e Delltones]] (5), \"[[Hello, Dolly! (song)|Hello, Dolly!]]\" by [[Louis Armstrong]] (5), and \"[[It Hurts to Be in Love]]\" by [[Gene Pitney]] (6).\n\nHits by Australasian artists included \"The Crusher\" by [[The Atlantics]], \"When You're Not to Wear\" by [[Rob E.G.]], \"She Wears My Ring\" / \"Let's Love Tonight\" by [[Johnny O'Keefe]], \"Mashed Potato\" / \"Don't Cha Know\" by [[Billy Thorpe and the Aztecs]], and \"4,003,221 Tears From Now\" by [[Judy Stone]].\n\n==1965==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! | Date\n! | Artist\n! | Single\n! | Weeks at number one\n|-\n|2 January\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=5|[[The Beatles]]\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=5|\"[[I Feel Fine]]\" / \"[[She's a Woman]]\"\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=5| 8 weeks\n|-\n|9 January\n|-\n|16 January\n|-\n|23 January\n|-\n|30 January\n|-\n|6 February\n|align=\"center\"|[[Julie Rogers (singer)|Julie Rogers]]\n|align=\"center\"|\"[[The Wedding (song)|The Wedding]]\"\n|align=\"center\"| 1 week\n|-\n|13 February\n|align=\"center\"|[[Petula Clark]]\n|align=\"center\"|\"[[Downtown (Petula Clark song)|Downtown]]\"\n|align=\"center\"| 1 week\n|-\n|20 February\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=3|[[The Rolling Stones]]\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=3|\"[[Under the Boardwalk]]\" / \"[[Walking the Dog]]\"\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=3| 3 weeks\n|-\n|27 February\n|-\n|6 March\n|-\n|13 March\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=3|[[The Seekers]] {{flagicon|Australia}}\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=3|\"[[I'll Never Find Another You]]\"\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=3| 3 weeks\n|-\n|20 March\n|-\n|27 March\n|-\n|3 April\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=7|[[The Beatles]]\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=4|\"[[Rock and Roll Music]]\" / \"[[Honey Don't]]\"\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=4| 4 weeks\n|-\n|10 April\n|-\n|17 April\n|-\n|24 April\n|-\n|1 May\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=3|\"[[Ticket to Ride]]\" / \"[[Yes It Is]]\"\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=3| 3 weeks\n|-\n|8 May\n|-\n|15 May\n|-\n|22 May\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=4|[[Herman's Hermits]]\n|align=\"center\" r